title: Abstraction Point: Null Reality Volume 1
description:
The Abstraction Point (http://www.abstractionpoint.net) presents to you their first official album. Null Productions brings you a funky mix of some housey-trancey grooves.

This is the full CD-quality release. It is released under the terms of the Creative Commons BY-NC-SA 3.0 license.

For more of our material, please visit our forums at http://forum.abstractionpoint.net and go to the Beat Exchange board.

Thanks for your support!
